Package cs.eng1.piazzapanic.food.ingredients

Class BasicCookable

java.lang.Object
cs.eng1.piazzapanic.food.ingredients.Ingredient
cs.eng1.piazzapanic.food.ingredients.BasicCookable
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cookable, Holdable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Potato, UncookedPizza
public abstract class BasicCookable extends Ingredient implements Cookable
A base class for ingredients that need to be cooked, such as Potato. Implements the Cookable interface to enable the chopping functionality.
Author:
Ross Holmes, Andrey Samoilov
